<section class="fullpage bio top-edge bottom-edge" id="section-bio">

  <header class="header__section">
    <h3 class="title__section title__name">
      <span class="letter-spacing">Alex</span><span class="letter-spacing">Sachel</span>
    </h3>
  </header>
  <main class="container__bio">
    <figure class="bio image__top-left">
      <picture>
        {% set image_path %}/images/Bio-Alex-Sachel-Style-Consultant{% endset %}
        <img
          alt="An image of Alex Sachel, a Style Consultant based out of Chattanooga, TN."
          {% include "partials/ri-med-width.njk" %}
          >
      </picture>
    </figure>
    <p class="paragraph__first">
      <span class="first-letter">ACS</span> Wardrobe Consulting launched two years ago in Chattanooga, TN and has now grown into a second office based in San Antonio, TX. I started ACS after acquiring over a decade of experience in the luxury retail industry in NYC, while working hand in hand with women who I watched be instantly transformed after a simple outfit change. I knew that a full service styling agency was not only necessary outside of a big city, but also nearly impossible to find in smaller markets... until now!
    </p>
    <p>
      With ACS Wardrobe Consulting, I focus on building and organizing every client's wardrobe to better suit their unique daily needs and lifestyle. Services for both men and women include closet organization, personal shopping, event styling, travel packing, closet design, and much more. We strive to not merely outfit clients but take the deliberation and stress out of daily dressing. More importantly we educate clients along the way so that they can develop a deep understanding of their own personal style and gain confidence through that awareness. To me, teaching the “why” is critically important in meeting both of these needs.
    </p>
    <p>
      It’s imperative for me to equip each client with the tools needed to dress for their body type, their unique proportions, their profession, and their lifestyle, all while streamlining decisions & maximizing efficiency each and every day.
      </span>
    </p>
  </main>
  <footer class="footer__section">
    <div class="pullquote__bio pullquote__brand">
      <h2 class="title__brand-quote letter-spacing">
        I truly believe in the transformative power of a great outfit.
      </h2>
    </div>
  </footer>
</section>